 neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color:#374955;\">What happens if I need additional hours?</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n														<ul style=\"color:#8b59a4; list-style: square; padding-left: 15px;\">\r\n															<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">If you know upfront you will need more hours, let us know before booking so we can send you a new quote and secure the requested time</span></span></li>\r\n															<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">It may be possible for the packers to stay for additional time on the day, subject to their availability</span></span></li>\r\n															<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">For additional time requested, the rate is $60 inc. GST per packer per hour, billed in 15 minute increments</span></span></li>\r\n														</ul>\r\n													</td>\r\n												</tr>\r\n											</tbody></table>\r\n											<!--[if mso]>\r\n												</td>\r\n											<![endif]-->\r\n											\r\n											<!--[if mso]>\r\n												</tr>\r\n												</table>\r\n											<![endif]-->\r\n										</td>\r\n									</tr>\r\n								</tbody>\r\n							</table><table class=\"mcnImageBlock\" style=\"min-width:100%;\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n								<tbody class=\"mcnImageBlockOuter\">\r\n									<tr>\r\n										<td style=\"padding:0px\" class=\"mcnImageBlockInner\" valign=\"top\">\r\n											<table class=\"mcnImageContentContainer\" style=\"min-width:100%;\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" align=\