(5, '1', 3, 'Send Follow Up email for Home', 'info@hireamover.com.au', '', '', 'info@hireamover.com.au', 'RE: Good news - we\'re available!', ' <style type=\"text/css\">.follow-table-email-first p{margin-bottom:10px;} body { font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial; margin: 0px; font-size: 12px; } pre.mscrmpretag { word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap;} </style><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_forms/controls/controls.css.aspx\"><div><style>@font-face {font-family: Calibri;}@font-face {font-family: Lato-Regular;}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal {margin: 0cm;margin-bottom: .0001pt;font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;}</style><style>html, body{ color: #393939; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background:#e9e9e9; }html, body, p, td{ font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; color: #393939; }	p{ margin-bottom: 15px;color: #393939; }</style><table class=\"follow-table-email-first\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" align=\"left\"><p><font face=\"Arial\">Hi {{clientfirstname}},</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">I just wanted to touch base about the quote we sent you below. Did you \r\nwant to go ahead and lock in the move or do you have some questions I \r\ncan help you with?</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">If you did want to book it in, please click on this <a href=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/secure-payment?id={{uuid}}&amp;amt={{amt}}\">link</a> to enter your address information.</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">If you\'ve made other arrangements it would be great if you could let me know so I can book in the time with someone else.</font></p><p></p><p></p><p><font face=\"Arial\">Kind regards,</font></p><p></p><p style=\"color:#1F497D\"><b><font face=\"Arial\">{{sendername}}<br>Hire A Mover</font></b></p><p style=\"color:#1F497D\"><font face=\"Arial\">1300 358 700<br>info@hireamover.com.au<br>www.hireamover.com.au</font></p><p></p><hr></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\r