-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">The one-off call-out fee is a single charge that helps cover some of the cost of our movers getting to your origin address and then back from your final address</span></span></li>\r\n														<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">The hourly rate begins when we arrive at your pick-up address and ends when we finish at the destination address</span></span></li>\r\n														<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">Once you have made your $50 deposit you will receive a booking confirmation within 12 hours</span></span></li>\r\n														<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">A minimum of 2 hours applies on all jobs - we charge in 15 minute increments</span></span></li>\r\n													</ul>\r\n													<p style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color:#374955;\"><strong>Payment terms</strong></span></p>\r\n													<ul style=\"color:#0099ce; list-style: square;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n														<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">Final payment must be settled on the day of the move in cash or Visa/MasterCard (we do not accept cheques)</span></span></li>\r\n														<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">Should you wish to cancel your booking, your deposit is fully refundable up to 48 hours prior to your scheduled move</span></span></li>\r\n													</ul>\r\n													<p style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color:#374955;\">Insurance policy</span></strong></p>\r\n													\r\n													<ul style=\"color:#0099ce; list-style: square;\">\r\n														<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">Whilst the work of our removalist team is covered under our insurance policy, we recommend you take insurance for your move for things outside our control. You can obtain a quote <a href=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/insurance\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#4480c9;\">here</a><br></span></span></li>\r\n													</ul>\r\n													<p style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color:#374955;\">How long will my move take?</span></strong></p>\r\n													\r\n													<ul style=\"color:#0099ce; list-style: square;margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n														<li style=\"margin-bottom:7px;\"><span style=\"color:#374955\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;line-height: 23px; font-size:17px;\">Every move is different and depends on numerous factors including access, parking and how much furniture you have. A typical 1 bedroom property takes 2-4 hours, 2 bedroom property takes 4-6 hours, 3 bedroom property takes 5-7 hours and a 4 bedroom property 7-10 hours.</span></span></li>\r\n													</ul>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n											</tbody></table>\r\n											<!--[if mso]>\r\n												</td>\r\n											<![endif]-->\r\n											\r\n											<!--[if mso]>\r\n												</tr>\r\n						