b(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">Thank you for choosing Hire A Mover for your upcoming move.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">We pride ourselves on offering a professional and friendly service and want to ensure your moving day is as stress-free as possible.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; background-color: transparent;\">HIRE A MOVER - BOOKING CONFIRMATION</span><br></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #1f497d;font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; background-color: transparent;\">1. MOVING DATE AND ESTIMATED TIME OF ARRIVAL</span><br></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><span title=\"Body Datatime  e.g. 1-3pm on 27/09/2017\"><strong>{{datetime}}</strong></span><strong></strong></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">We have your dedicated removals team booked in for this date and time. <b>Please be aware that the above time may vary slightly due to unforeseen issues such as traffic, weather, or a prior job delay.</b> Please be patient if we are held up in any way and we will try and advise you as early as possible.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">If you experience any issues, please phone our customer service team on 1300 358 700 and if there is no answer, leave a detailed voice message and we will call you back ASAP.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #1f497d;font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;\">2. MOVING FROM AND TO:</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><strong>Moving from: </strong><span title=\"Moving from street\"><strong>{{movingfromstreet}}</strong></span><span title=\"Moving from postcode\"></span><span title=\"Moving from suburb\"><strong>{{movingfromsuburb}}</strong>, </span><strong></strong><span title=\"Moving from suburb\"></span><span title=\"Moving from suburb\"><strong>{{movingfromstate}}</strong></span><span title=\"Moving from postcode\">, </span><span title=\"Moving from postcode\"><strong>{{movingfrompostcode}}</strong></span><span title=\"Moving from suburb\"></span><span title=\"Moving from postcode\"><br></span><strong>Moving </strong><strong>to:&nbsp;</strong><span title=\"Moving to street\"><strong>{{movingtostreet}}</strong></span><strong> </strong><span title=\"Moving to postcode\"><strong></strong></span><span title=\"Moving to suburb\"><strong>{{movingtosuburb}}</strong>, </span><span title=\"Moving to state\"><strong>{{movingtostate}}, </strong></span><span title=\"Moving to suburb\"></span><span title=\"Moving to postcode\"><strong>{{movingtopostcode}}</strong></span><span title=\"Moving to suburb\"><br></span><span title=\"Additional Pickup\"><strong>{{additionalpickup}}</strong></span><span title=\"Additional Delivery\"><strong>{{additionaldelivery}}</strong></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><span title=\"Additional Delivery\"><span style=\"color: #1f497d; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; background-color: transparent;\">3. RATE - QUOTATION</span><strong><br></strong></span></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">The quotation given to you for your upcoming move with \r\n                                            <span title=\"No of Mover e.g. 2\">{{noofmover}}</span> removalists and <span title=\"No of Truck e.g. 1\">{{nooftruck}}</span> truck is <b>$</b><span title=\"Hourly Rate e.g. $120.00\"><strong>{{hourlyrate}}</strong></span><strong></strong> including GST per hour with a one-off call-out&nbsp; charge of <span title=\"Travel Fee e.g. $80.00\"><strong>${{tavelfee}}</strong></span><strong></strong>. Please keep in mind this is not a fixed price, it is an hourly rate.&nbsp; Please note a minimum 2 hour charge applies to all bookings. Thereafter we charge in 15 minute increments.<span title=\"Additional charges\"><strong>{{additionalcharges}}</strong></span> <br></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #1f497d;font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;\">4. PAYMENT &amp; DEPOSIT</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">A ${{amt}} deposit has been taken to secure your booking. This will be deducted from the final payment on the day of your move. The full amount due (less deposit) is due on completion of the move by cash or credit card. Please ensure that you have payment available on the day in either cash or with a Visa/Mastercard.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #1f497d; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">5. IMPORTANT INFORMATION TO PREPARE FOR YOUR MOVE</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">Please pack as many of your items as possible into boxes. The more individual items there are, the longer the move will take. If you still require boxes or packing supplies, order them online at <a href=\"https://www.hireabox.com.au/\">Hire A Box</a> using the below discount code (excludes ACT &amp; QLD)</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">If you have any particularly large or heavy items (over 3metres or 80kg) please let us know prior to the move. If you have any items that are fragile, please point them out to the movers on the day. </p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">Bed frames and large furniture such as IKEA wardrobes that have been assembled inside your home may need to be disassembled. Our movers carry basic tools.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">Please ensure appliances are disconnected from power and taps, etc. Our removalists are not plumbers or electricians and will not warrant any of these tasks including reconnecting these appliances. You may need to organise a plumber or electrician to check these appliances.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #1f497d; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">6. ACCEPTANCE OF THE TERMS AND CONDITIONS</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">This confirms that you have accepted the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/terms-conditions\">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>. Please ensure you have read both this booking confirmation and the terms and conditions and if you have any issues or concerns, please let us know prior to your booking commencement time.</span></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #1f497d;font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://www.hireabox.com.au/?utm_source=HAM%20Booking%20Email&amp;utm_medium=Email&amp;utm_campaign=HAM%20BOOKING%20EMAIL\" style=\"font-family: Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><img style=\"width: 500px;\" src=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/wp-content/uploads/bookingconfirmation_discount_1.jpg\" alt=\"Booking Confirmation Discount\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\"></a><a href=\"https://www.hireapacker.com.au/?utm_source=HAM%20Booking%20Email&amp;utm_medium=Email&amp;utm_campaign=HAM%20BOOKING%20EMAIL\" style=\"font-family: Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><img style=\"width: 500px;\" src=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/wp-content/uploads/bookingconfirmation_discount_2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Discount\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\"></a><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Bookings Department</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>Hire A Mover</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>p</span></b><span>&nbsp;1300 358 700</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>e</span></b><span>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@hireamover.com.au\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: black\">info@hireamover.com.au</span></a></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>w</span></b><span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: black\">www.hireamover.com.au</span></a></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><img src=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/logo.png\" alt=\"signature-logo\" width=\"168\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin:10px 0\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: #7f7f7f\">This email and any attachments are confidential. If you are not the intended recipient, you must not disclose or use the information contained in it. If you have received this email in error, please notify</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: black\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"mailto:info@hireamover.com.au\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Tahoma\">Hire A Mover</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: black\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: #7f7f7f\">immediately by return email and delete the document.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: black\"><u></u><u></u></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: #00b050\">P</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: black\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: #7f7f7f\">Please consider the environment, think of those polar bears on YouTube and don\'t print this e-mail&nbsp;unless you really need to.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: black\"><u></u><u></u></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></td><td width=\"35\" valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div>', 0, 0, '2017-11-10 12:15:31'),
