(20, '3', 5, 'Send Booking Confirmation email for Interstate', 'info@hireamover.com.au', '', '', 'info@hireamover.com.au', 'Booking Confirmation - {{clientfirstname}} - {{subjectdatetime}}', '<style type=\"text/css\"> body { font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial; margin: 0px; position: absolute; height: 95%; width: 95%; font-size: 12px; } pre.mscrmpretag { word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap;} </style><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_forms/controls/controls.css.aspx\"><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><style>body {font-family: \"Geneva\", sans-serif; line-height: 20px;}</style><title>Hire A Box - Hire Confirmation Letter</title><div style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><table width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"background-color:#E97B00;\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#53636e;\" align=\"center\"><br><table width=\"583\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" align=\"left\"><table width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"35\" valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</td><td valign=\"top\" align=\"left\"><table width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td cellpadding=\"10\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding: 10px 10px 10px 10px;font-family:Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#525252;\" valign=\"top\" align=\"left\"><style>@font-face {font-family: Calibri;}@font-face {font-family: Lato-Regular;}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal {margin: 0cm;margin-bottom: .0001pt;font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;}</style><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">Hi <span title=\"Client Firstname  e.g. Brett\">{{clientfirstname}}</span>,</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">Thank you for choosing Hire A Mover for your upcoming move.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">We pride ourselves on offering a professional and friendly service and want to ensure your moving day is as stress-free as possible.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">To give you a clear understanding of the service you have booked, please find below your booking confirmation with all the relevant details.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;font-size: 16pt;font-weight: bold;\">HIRE A MOVER - BOOKING CONFIRMATION</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;font-size: 16pt;font-weight: bold;\">INTERSTATE MOVE</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #ed7d31;font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;\">1. CONFIRMING YOUR PICK UP AND DELIVERY DATE AND ACCEPTING THE TERMS AND CONDITIONS</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><strong>This booking confirmation confirms your booking for the below date and time. It also confirms that you have accepted the <a href=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/terms-conditions\">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>. Please ensure you have read both this booking confirmation and the terms and conditions and if you have any issues or concerns, please let us know prior to your booking commencement time.</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #ed7d31;font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;\">2. COLLECTION AND DELIVERY DATE </p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><strong>Collection: {{subjectdatetime}}</strong><br><strong>Delivery: {{subjectdatetime}}</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">Please note it is very difficult to give you an exact time for the collection or delivery of your goods. The reason for this is because our interstate trucks are large and have a number of collections and deliveries along the way. Any delay in these or other unforseen factors, will mean your collection/delivery time may change. You will receive a phone call or SMS prior to lunchtime on the day advising you what time our truck will arrive. We recommend you keep both days free as there can be unforseen delays. If you experience any issues, please contact us on 1300 358 700 during business hours, or after-hours on 0405 776 667. If there is no answer, leave a voicemail and we will return your call.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #ed7d31;font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;\">3. MOVING FROM AND TO:</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><strong>Pickup from:</strong><span title=\"Moving from suburb\"><strong> {{movingfromsuburb}}</strong></span><strong>, </strong>                                            <span title=\"Moving from postcode\"><strong>{{movingfrompostcode}}</strong>, </span><span title=\"Moving from state\"><strong>{{movingfromstate}}</strong></span><strong><br></strong></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\"><strong>Delivery to: </strong><span title=\"Moving from suburb\"><strong>{{movingtosuburb}}</strong></span><strong>, </strong>                                            <span title=\"Moving from postcode\"><strong>{{movingtopostcode}}</strong>, </span><span title=\"Moving from state\"><strong>{{movingtostate}}</strong></span><strong><br></strong><strong><br></strong></p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">Please make sure that all your packing boxes are clearly labelled with your name and mobile number. Please also ensure all your goods are packaged and protected adequately for transport. Failure to do so may result in damage in which Hire A Mover will not be held responsible for (refer <a href=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/terms-conditions\">Terms &amp; Conditions</a> for more information here). If you have any sensitive or delicate items, give our office a call now on 1300 358 700 if you have not already notified us about these.</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #ed7d31;font-size: 14pt;font-weight: bold;\">4. RATE - QUOTATION</p><p style=\"font-family: Calibri, Geneva, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 84, 106); line-height: 1.4;\">The quotation for your upcoming move with                                             <span title=\"No of Mover e.g. 2\">{{noofmover}}</span> removalists and <span title=\"No of Truck e.g. 1\">{{nooftruck}}</span> truck is $<span title=\"Initial sell price\">{{initialsellprice}}</span> including a pre-paid deposit of $<b>\r\n</b>                                            <span title=\"Amount e.g. $50.00\">{{amt}}</span>. Note that the remainder of the payment is due on collection of your goods by credit card. Please read our <a href=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/terms-conditions\">Terms &amp; Conditions</a> relating to payment, additional charges and deposits for further information.</p><a href=\"https://www.hireabox.com.au/?utm_source=HAM%20Booking%20Email&amp;utm_medium=Email&amp;utm_campaign=HAM%20BOOKING%20EMAIL\"><img style=\"width: 500px;\" src=\"https://www.hireamover.com.au/wp-content/uploads/bookingconfirmation_discount_1.jpg\" alt=\"Booking Confirmation Discount\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\"></a><a href=\"https:/