pan style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: black\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: #7f7f7f\">Please consider the environment, think of those polar bears on YouTube and don\'t print this e-mail&nbsp;unless you really need to.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Tahoma; color: black\"><u></u><u></u></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></td><td width=\"35\" valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div>', 0, 0, '2017-11-10 15:43:19'),
